<LegalLayout title="Refund Policy" updated="2026-07-01">
  <p>This Refund Policy explains when refunds are and are not available for purchases made through Exclusive Mentorship.</p>
  <h2>Full bundle (Tier 2)</h2>
  <p>The full bundle is covered by a 7-day money-back guarantee. If you are not satisfied, contact us within 7 days of your purchase date to request a full refund. Refunds are processed to your original payment method.</p>
  <h2>Individual chapters (Tier 1)</h2>
  <p>Individual chapter (chapter-by-chapter) purchases are final and non-refundable, because access to the content is granted immediately upon purchase.</p>
  <h2>How to request a refund</h2>
  <p>REPLACE — add your contact email or support method here. Include your order reference when contacting us.</p>
  <h2>Exceptions</h2>
  <p>REPLACE — note any local consumer-law rights that may apply and any anti-abuse conditions (e.g. repeated refund requests).</p>
</LegalLayout>
